Version 0.3.1
(6 December 2004)
http://svn.klencke.net/svn/libip_udp/tags/0.3.1
-----------------------------------------------

- Clearer wording in HTML output.
- Fix segfault in inet_checksum when called
  when buf[buflen] is at an unallocated page
  and buflen is odd. (hardly ever happens)


Version 0.3
(5 December 2004)
http://svn.klencke.net/svn/libip_udp/tags/0.3
---------------------------------------------

- Show corrupt/dropped packets in simplelog
  using different colors.
- XML logger with XSLT transformation for
  HTML output added.
- Listening UDP socket uses SO_REUSEADDR to
  fix problems on some systems.


Version 0.2
(22 October 2004)
http://svn.klencke.net/svn/libip_udp/tags/0.2
---------------------------------------------

- Packet Loss
- Simple Monitor Tool
- ANSI C Compile Fix
- Specify real peer IP address
- Specify real log IP address


